NEW RULES AGREED UPON IN 1849; REVISED 1863.

I.-The Society shall consist of not more than three hundred and fifty members.

[L—There shall be a Patron of the Society, who shall be President.

[IL—There shall be twenty-four Vice-Presidents, a Secre- tary, and Two TreasurerS.
